Name: Myst V: End of Ages
About the game: The Grand Finale of the greatest adventure! Decide the fate of a civilization in this triumphant final chapter to the Myst saga. Embark on an epic journey into the heart of a shattered empire as the only explorer who can still save it— or destroy it with the wrong choices. Whether you’re a longtime Myst fan or new to the series, the Grand Finale is an epic adventure you won’t want to miss. Key features: Developed by the original creators of Myst: Rand Miller and Cyan Worlds bring you the ultimate chapter in a series already renowned as the pinnacle of adventure gaming. Explore vast 3D worlds with an easy click of the mouse: Improved point-and-click interface offers several options to accommodate your exploration style. Interact with the world like never before: The innovative new slate lets you communicate with mysterious creatures and manipulate the world around you. The characters of Myst brought to life: New facial mapping technology brings characters to life with unprecedented emotion and expressiveness.
